	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I have a 2005 Toshiba CRT television that has served me faithfully. However, I have recently been getting a wierd dark spot near the top left corner of the display. Does anyone here know what exactly this is/a possible fix? This TV isn't that old, and it's not burn-in in the traditional sense, although it may be deterioration. It's a nice big 27&quot; display, so I'd prefer not to have to find a new(ish) one.

		

		</td>
